serious land owner issues that could potentially shut the creek down to all kayakers. It would be<br/>
horrible to lose access to a gem of a creek such as bottoms. Lets not mess up relations with the<br/>
land owners, we do not want this river to go to waste like Johns has. Be Safe out there...and watch<br/>
for wood below two blind mice, it tends to collect on the bottoms section. </div>
